page.title: 11A 10 YEAR OLDS DAY
page.content: At 06:45 I shake the covers off me and I go to wake my Dad. Then I have breakfast - Rice Krispies and marmalade sandwiches. After breakfast I brush my teeth and get dressed. I go downstairs and watch Popeye or a video. When that is finished I do my homework. Then I grab my bag and coat and rush to the car. My Mum takes me, on her way to work, to the coach. I get on a bus in Tilehurst to take me to Englefield Primary School. The journey takes 25 minutes. After school finishes at 15:40 I go straight home and I watch television until tea at 17:00. Afterwards I go to Cub Scouts with my friends.
